ges]]\n* [[\u0141a\u0144cut Castle]]\n* [http://rogalin.mnp.art.pl/en/page/carriage-house-and-stable Rogalin Palace]\n\n===Portugal===\n* [[National Coach Museum (Lisbon)|National Coach Museum (''Museu dos Coches'')]], Lisbon<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.museudoscoches-ipmuseus.pt/en/coleccao.htm|title=NCM \u2013 Collection.|publisher=|accessdate=12 February 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Geraz do Lima Carriage museum]]\n\n===Spain===\n* [[Carriage Museum, Seville|Carriage Museum]], Seville\n\n===United Kingdom===\n* [[Mossman Collection]], Luton, Bedfordshire<ref>[http://www.luton.gov.uk/internet/Leisure_and_culture/Museums_and_galleries/Stockwood%20Park/The%20Mossman%20Carriage%20Collection Mossman Collection Website] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080422020121/http://www.luton.gov.uk/internet/Leisure_and_culture/Museums_and_galleries/Stockwood%20Park/The%20Mossman%20Carriage%20Collection |date=22 April 2008 }}</ref>\n* [[Royal Mews]] at Buckingham Palace, London.<ref>[http://www.royalinsight.gov.uk/output/Page5023.asp Royal Mews] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517111142/http://www.royalinsight.gov.uk/output/Page5023.asp |date=17 May 2008 }}</ref>\n* Swingletree Carriage Collection. John Parker Swingletree Carriage Driving, Swingletree, Wingfield, Nr. Diss, Norfolk<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.swingletree.co.uk/carriages(1).htm|title=SWINGLETREE CARRIAGE COLLECTION|website=www.swingletree.co.uk|accessdate=12 February 2019}}</ref>\n* National Trust Carriage Museum, [[Arlington Court]], near [[Barnstaple]], Devon<ref>[http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/main/w-arlington-carriage-list.pdf National Trust Carriage Museum] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121205215/http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/main/w-arlington-carriage-list.pdf |date=21 November 2010 }}</ref>\n* The [[Tyrwhitt-Drake Museum of Carriages]], Maidstone, Kent<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.museum.maidstone.gov.uk/tyrwhittdrake/|title=The Tyrwhitt-Drake Museum of Carri