ain/w-arlington-carriage-list.pdf National Trust Carriage Museum] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121205215/http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/main/w-arlington-carriage-list.pdf |date=21 November 2010 }}</ref>\n* The [[Tyrwhitt-Drake Museum of Carriages]], Maidstone, Kent<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.museum.maidstone.gov.uk/tyrwhittdrake/|title=The Tyrwhitt-Drake Museum of Carriages|accessdate=12 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716233913/http://www.museum.maidstone.gov.uk/tyrwhittdrake/|archive-date=16 July 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n*The worlds only horse-drawn Rainbow Hearse<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elegant-carriages.com/|title=Horse Drawn Carriage Hire - Weddings and Funerals in Chorley|website=www.elegant-carriages.com|access-date=2020-01-20}}</ref>\n\n===United States===\n[[File:Crossing the Mississippi on the Ice by C.C.A. Christensen.png|thumb|Crossing the [[Mississippi]] on the ice, 19th century]]\n* Florida Carriage Museum, Weirsdale, Florida. Formerly Austin Carriage Museum.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fcmr.org/|title=Florida Carriage Museum & Resort|publisher=|accessdate=12 February 2019}}</ref>\n* Skyline Farm Carriage Museum, North Yarmouth, Maine<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skylinefarm.org/|title=SkylineFarm|website=www.skylinefarm.org|accessdate=12 February 2019}}</ref>\n* The Carriage Collection of the Owls Head Transportation Museum, Owls Head, Maine.<ref>[http://www.ohtm.org/carr_page.html The Carriage Collection of the Owls Head Transportation Museum] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080515144828/http://www.ohtm.org/carr_page.html |date=15 May 2008 }}</ref>\n* The Carriage Museum, Washington, Kentucky<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonky.com/carriage_museum.htm|title=The Carriage Museum|website=www.washingtonky.com|accessdate=12 February 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Carriage Museum of America]], Lexington, Kentucky<ref>{{cite web|url=http://carriagemuseumlibrary.org/|title=Carriage Mus