st1=Rebekah |title=Forever 35 Is the Self-Care Podcast You Didn't Know You Needed |url=https://www.houstoniamag.com/style-and-shopping/2018/05/forever-35-podcast |accessdate=9 April 2020 |work=Houstonia Magazine |date=17 May 2018}}</ref> Huffington post writer Jillian Capewell praised the podcast for sounding: \"like you\u2019re eavesdropping on a conversation between your friends.\"<ref name=\"Capewell\">{{cite news |last1=Capewell |first1=Jillian |title=We Listened To A Lot Of Podcasts In 2018. Here Are 31 We Loved. |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.ca/entry/favorite-podcasts-2018_n_5bf5a953e4b0771fb6b571e7?ri18n=true |accessdate=9 April 2020 |work=HuffPost Canada |date=29 November 2018 |language=en}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Interview podcasts]]\n[[Category:Talk podcasts]]\n", "name_user": "Archivalistic", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added a space after a period :)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Forever35"}
